products.title: BEDSURE Large Dog Bed for Large Dogs Up to 75lbs - Big Orthopedic Dog Beds with Removable Washable Cover, Egg Crate Foam Pet Bed Mat, Dark Grey
features: Designed for Pets: The classic pet bed mattress design gives your fluffy friend plenty of room to sprawl out and get cozy in any position. Easy to carry and ideal for use indoors and outside, in a crate, in your car, or wherever life takes you.

All-Seasons Bed: The two-sided design features warm and cozy sherpa with a reverse side of cool and soft Oxford fabric. Durable and suitable for all-season usekeep your dog cool in summer and warm in winter for increased comfort.

Orthopedic Support: Designed to give your pet unparalleled support for a deep, dreamy sleep. High-density egg-crate foam distributes weight evenly and provides the perfect amount of pressure relief to reduce joint pain and arthritis discomfort.
Pet-Safe Materials: CertiPUR-US certified foam and luxury sherpa come together to create a dog bed that is as safe as it is comfortable.
Easy Care Removable Cover: Featuring an easy-to-remove, durable, and stain-resistant cover that makes deep cleaning a breeze. Simply machine wash and tumble dry.
